                "key": "Unfinished Masterpiece",
                "string_values": [
                  "<p>When using an Elemental Skill, All Elemental DMG Bonus will be increased by <span style=\"color: rgb(55, 255, 255)\">8%/10%/12%/14%/16%</span> for 15s, and a Bond of Life worth 24% of Max HP will be granted. This effect can be triggered once every 10s. When the Bond of Life is cleared, every 1,000 HP cleared in the process will provide <span style=\"color: rgb(55, 255, 255)\">2%/2.5%/3%/3.5%/4%</span> All Elemental DMG Bonus, up to a maximum of <span style=\"color: rgb(55, 255, 255)\">12%/15%/18%/21%/24%</span>. This effect lasts 15s.</p>"
